Room.Name: Back Alley
Room.ShortDescription: You are in a wide alley which goes east and west behind Hafnia's best shops.
Room.LongDescription: There is an entry, or exit depending on your point of view, to the west. The south side of the alley seems to be a series of locked doors, but on the north side you see several municipal offices and warehouses. This alley is not very clean. You would think the city would be embarrassed.
